{"tid":2345263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佛教醫院內科病房女護士初步確診　曾與5醫院10名醫護食飯","createTime":"2020-12-29T11:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T11:44:46.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40fc449d80fb5ea9617850705c31eab5cbde959a","tid":2345263,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:07:09.000Z","msg":"佛教醫院內科病房再多一名女護士初步確診感染新型冠狀病毒，她曾經照顧一名後來確診的病人，協助病人留取深喉唾液樣本，期間有戴外科口罩及手套，但無戴面罩。醫管局指，這名護士上星期四的病毒檢測結果呈陰性反應，她昨日發燒，再做檢測發現是陽性。 <br />\n<br />\n醫管局又指，初步確診的護士，曾<span class=\"red\">與10名醫護食飯，其中5人同於佛教醫院工作，其餘分別在兒童醫院、東區醫院、仁濟醫院及伊利沙伯醫院工作</span>，全部被列為密切接觸者。醫管局提醒醫護合作，疫情期間避免聚餐，減低病毒傳播風險。"},{"pid":"dacf5410803d2e1bd82d1c4da2e1787df278b6da","tid":2345263,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a9c8ac5f8ba3b1832d7d231a257a97559fb18d","tid":2345263,"uid":190789,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"而家鬼撚知自己中咩？<br />\n政府唔封關咪攬炒囉，dklm"},{"pid":"ccce120a6db9a1e74c725eadfef47fc5708fafd7","tid":2345263,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"個4間醫院再爆"},{"pid":"de48d73854aff1b3f23aeebf192745496e85e430","tid":2345263,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"鄭7鵝成功放毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2e5aae614a3b039513ad20cf50db5e2e7a1125","tid":2345263,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"de48d73854aff1b3f23aeebf192745496e85e430","tid":2345263,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"鄭7鵝成功放毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gi